
<h1>Come Live With Us</h1>
<h2>Fascinating experiences with fascinating people</h2>
<p><em>People are awesome!</em> That's what we believe. At Come Live With Us you can visit with interesting people from all walks of life. Sign up to spend time with circus performers, preeminent researchers, famous entertainers, successful entrepreneurs, and so much more! Check out a few of the experiences we have to offer: </p>

<div class="card-container">
  <div class="row">
    <% @apartments.each do |apartment| %>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3">
          <%= link_to apartment_path(apartment.id) do %>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="gradient">
                <h1><%= apartment.name %></h1>
                <img src=<%= apartment.photos %> >
                <p><%= apartment.description %></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

<%= link_to "upload your nifty new experience", new_apartment_path, class:"btn btn-success" %>

